snippet.title: Shredders is dropping March 17th! 🤟
snippet.description:
Our best worst kept secret: 
Shredders is coming March 17! 🤟

Fire up your Xbox Series X|S, PC, Steam or Xbox Game Pass, it's (nearly) Shredding time!

Check it all out at https://shreddersgame.com
